data.description: Welcome to this beautiful historical multi-family home in the Donaldson Terrace area with spacious sized rooms and a generously size lot! The home offers 3 complete separate units with their own kitchen and master bedrooms. Unit 4 (Formerly detached garage) is a 1/1 is not 100% complete, however, has running water and electricity, which offers maximum income potential for the new owner to have a 4th unit making this opportunity a quadplex. The home is located with easy access to I-10 and I-410. The home offers crown molding, a spacious driveway that fits 8 vehicles and also includes a lovely gazebo in the back yard.
